# Code owners for the security/infra blast radius.
#
# With branch protection "Require review from Code Owners" enabled on `main`,
# these paths cannot be merged without the owner's review. `@Solurix` is the repo
# owner — change it to the actual reviewer handle or a team if that org uses teams.

# CI/CD & the preview pipeline (holds the WIF trust + deploy steps).
/.github/workflows/**    @Solurix
/.github/CODEOWNERS       @Solurix

# The image the build SA executes.
**/Dockerfile            @Solurix

# Build config that bakes NEXT_PUBLIC_* (incl. the API URL) into the image.
/next.config.mjs         @Solurix

# Dependencies = supply chain.
/package.json            @Solurix
/package-lock.json       @Solurix
